Result = int(input("Enter the date of the month : "))
day = Result % 7
if day == 0:
    print("The day is sunday")
elif day == 1:
    print("The day is Monday")
elif day == 2:
    print("The day is Tuesday")
elif day == 3:
    print("The day is Wed")
elif day == 4:
    print("The day is Thu")
elif day == 5:
    print("The day is Fri")
elif day == 6:
    print("The day is Sat")

Output :
Enter the date of the month : 23
The day is Tuesday
